model

Class OperatingSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.OperatingSystem

  • public class OperatingSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    AbstractModules use this class to define a list of operating systems where they are compatible with, and to validate if they can be executed on the current system. Allows the modules to define customized commands for different operating systems.
